                    "text": "The Mari Lwyd is out simply to enjoy the season. The Mari Lwyd's attacks have the <a aonid=\"188\" game-obj=\"Traits\">nonlethal</a> trait when attacking creatures, unless those creatures attempt a <a aonid=\"300\" game-obj=\"Rules\">hostile action</a> on the Mari Lwyd first."
