                    "name": "Persistent Wassailing",
                    "text": "The Mari Lwyd cannot be disrupted by common means. It always knows if a building is truly unoccupied or if the occupants can speak and hear and are merely refusing to sing back, and it is immune to <a aonid=\"287\" game-obj=\"Spells\"><i>silence</i></a> and similar effects of up to 5th level."
